</P>
<P>
How dare there be catcalls for winning jockey Eddie Delahoussaye. 
</P>
<P>
Shoemaker is enough of a man to have been outraged and embarrassed if the other 
riders had let him win, and Delahoussaye was only one of three who beat the 
Shoe. It doesn't lessen Shoemaker's accomplishments at all. 
