USSR; UNITED STATES -- TREATIES -- USSR; MX (MISSILE); STRATEGIC ARMS REDUCTION 
TALKS; NUCLEAR WEAPONS -- UNITED STATES; NUCLEAR WEAPONS -- USSR; MILITARY 
FORCE REDUCTIONS; DEFENSE SPENDING; UNITED STATES -- ARMED FORCES; UNITED 
