<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The father of Muhammad Ali, Cassius Marcellus Clay Sr., died at 77 after 
suffering a massive heart attack. 
</P>
<P>
Clay collapsed Thursday night as he was walking out of a department store in 
Louisville, Ky., and was dead on arrival at a hospital. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column; Obituary 
</P>
</TYPE>
