<DOCID> 174553 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
February 10, 1990, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 3; Column 6; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
30 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Bradley appointee -- A headline Friday misidentified Arthur R. Dansby as an 
ex-aide of Los Angeles Mayor Tom Bradley. Dansby is a former Bradley appointee 
to a city board. 
</P>
</TEXT>
